EotB Gem
========
Rails plugin which allow you easily track and observe your apps.

Installation
------------
$ gem install eotb

Using in your apps
------------------
Eotb.new("your_api_key", "host", "port") # default host and port are 127.0.0.1 and 3000 
Eotb.register_event(:user, :did_sth, { :user_name => "Vuvuzela" })

